Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱啊 小熊花名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 小熊小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真想把冰鎮鮭魚呲溜的吞下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好像素麵一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,流水鮭魚也不錯啊那麼風雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就和普通在河裡游的一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是中流擊水還是隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這有很大的區別喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好深奧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,當然深了 因為是河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小熊花名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小熊小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大會姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了這副打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,榮…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 花名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
