Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛 這胸針真漂亮
